Given this political fundraising email, respond with the name of the committee in the disclaimer that begins with Paid for by but does not include Paid for by, the committee address or the treasurer name. If no committee is present, return "None". Do not include any other text, no yapping.
name: CAPT Hung Cao
email: info@hungcaoforva.com
subject: 🚨Trump Rally Alert
body: Peter, President Trump is holding his LAST RALLY OF 2024 right here inVirginia, and I’m honored to stand alongside him! We’ve set a goal to raise$50,000 before the rally starts, and I told President Trump we could count onyou to pitch in. This final push will give us the resources we need to finishout this election and reach the final undecided voters. I don’t want to tellPresident Trump we MISSED our goal! Our rally starts in just a few hours, andwe’re running out of time. Can you pitch in now? PITCH IN NOW I knowPresident Trump appreciates all the work you’re putting in to take backVirginia! In Liberty, CAPT Hung Cao USN (Ret) TEXT HUNG TO 21412 Hung Cao:I’ll get right to the point - the Election is officially just days away, sowe’re launching an EMERGENCY ELECTION FUND to make sure we have the resourceswe need to win. I'm asking for your help today - whether you're able to give$5 or $25 today, any amount is greatly appreciated. DONATE NOW TO HELP WINOUR ELECTION & FLIP VIRGINIA RED JOIN TEAM CAO Paid for by Hung Cao forVirginia Use of military rank, job titles, and photographs in uniform does notimply endorsement by the Department of the Navy or the Department of Defense.Unsubscribe.
